snippet.title: Panta Rhei Demo | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Time is of the essence. Literally.
Venture into the everchanging Realm of Time and uncover a mystery that brought time itself to a halt. Fight your way through corrupted creatures in a challenging adventure roguelite where time is your best weapon.

Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1730550/Panta_Rhei/
